  Title: USER CONSENT
  Body: We collect limited data (such as device info and gameplay activity) to operate,
    improve, and analyze the app, and to provide relevant content or ads.\n\nBy tapping
    "Accept", you agree to this data use. Third-party services (e.g., analytics)
    may also process data. You can withdraw consent anytime in settings or by uninstalling
    the app.\n\nSee our Privacy Policy for details.
  Footer: Consent is required to continue.
